data.description: Charming and well maintained one story ranch style open concept home, located near the end of a quiet cul-de-sac. This home offers 3 bedrooms and an office/study that could be converted into a 4th bedroom. Living room, dining room, and primary bedroom all have hard wood flooring. The kitchen, primary bath, and secondary bath have all been remodeled. All major appliances are included. Washer/dryer, range, and dishwasher all replaced within the last five years. The roof was replaced in 2018 and the backyard fence was redone in 2020. This home has never flooded. Zoned to Katy ISD, one of the most prestigious school districts in the Houston area. The house location provides a convenient access to Katy Freeway, Westpark Tollway, and Grand Parkway. Minutes away from Katy Mills Mall, La Centerra, HEB, Kroger, CVS, Walgreens, and other dining, shopping and entertainment options. A very low tax rate.
